text: Karlie Kloss (born August 3, 1992) is an American model. Karlie Kloss was born in Chicago. She moved to St. Louis at age two. She was a Victoria's Secret Angel from 2013 to 2015. In 2015, she starred as Knockout in Taylor Swift's Bad Blood music video. ==References== Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Models from Chicago Category:People from St. Louis, Missouri
